# Ezee Fiber Internal Tools

Internal web app for Ezee Fiber technical support agents.

## Features
- **Note Generator** — Truck Roll Approval, Hard Down, Dispatch, CECR
- **Email Templates** — Equipment Return, Refer a Friend, Requesting Pictures, WiFi Security Key (Tachus & EzeeFiber)
- **Sticky Notes Panel** — persistent side panel, auto-saves to browser
- **Tech Region selector** — on Dispatch notes

