## Script Load Order
Scripts must load in this order (defined at bottom of index.html):
1. `data/oui-db.js` — data, no dependencies
2. `data/tech-regions.js` — data + populateTechRegionSelects()
3. `assets/js/helpers.js` — shared functions used by all note generators
4. `assets/js/app.js` — login, tabs (no feature dependencies)
5. `assets/js/truckroll.js` — depends on helpers.js
6. `assets/js/harddown.js` — depends on helpers.js
7. `assets/js/dispatch.js` — depends on helpers.js
8. `assets/js/cecr.js`
9. `assets/js/email.js`
10. `assets/js/notes.js`
11. `assets/js/init.js` — runs last, everything must be defined before this

## Deployment
This is a fully static site — no server or build step needed.
Host on GitHub Pages, Netlify, or any static file server.
Just make sure all files and folders are uploaded together.

## Adding a New Note Template
1. Add the HTML form to `index.html` inside a new `<div id="note-sub-yourname">` 
2. Add a nav button to the note sub-nav
3. Create `assets/js/yourname.js` with generate/copy/reset functions
4. Add `<script src="assets/js/yourname.js"></script>` before `init.js` in index.html
